headline: Royal Caribbean Group Raises Dividend Fifty Percent
summary: The Board of Directors of Royal Caribbean Group (NYSE: RCL) today declared a quarterly dividend of $1.50 per common share payable on April 3, 2026 to shareholders of record at the close of business on March 6, 2026.

headline: Are Wall Street Analysts Bullish on Royal Caribbean Cruises Stock?
